objects.name: resource.aspx
objects.description: This artifact is an ASPX webshell that is designed to execute remote JavaScript code on the system. The attacker must authenticate to the webshell client with the key "OWAwebconfig" before executing the remote code. The 'unsafe' context keyword is intentionally obfuscated to bypass security protocols.
